{"tid":177702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"20南亞漢旺角圍毆打死32歲同鄉　警改列謀殺","createTime":"2017-03-29T04:51:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T11:51:22.000Z","uid":20933,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a8b86f47d9f1d50e4e3cdd51cc63c90fdf22f1a","tid":177702,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:51:15.000Z","msg":"警方今日早上再拘捕多一名25歲南亞漢，與昨晚被捕兩名同鄉（25及26歲）涉嫌謀殺被扣查，警方正追緝其餘在逃兇徒，並安排驗屍，以確定死者的死因。 <br />\n<br />\n南亞假難民內訌釀命案，聲請巴漢遭同鄉鐵枝擊斃。一名持「行街紙」的巴基斯坦男子，上周六晚上，在大角咀街頭遭20名同鄉伏擊，其中4至5名南亞漢手持鐵枝向他狂毆，事主頭部重創，全身遍體鱗傷，延至昨午不治，警方列作謀殺案，由西九龍總區反黑組接手調查，當晚在大角咀拘捕一名持「行街紙」的巴漢，正追緝餘黨，相信死者得罪同鄉種下仇怨，有人糾結同鄉伏擊施以報復。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遇襲身亡的巴基斯坦男子AZIZ，32歲，以酷刑聲請名義提出免遣返申請，獲「行街紙」留港，與同鄉聚居於大角咀劏房。上周六晚上7時許，事主途經大角咀詩歌舞街休憩公園時遇伏，約20名南亞大漢衝出向他襲擊。據現場消息指，兇徒中有4、5人揮舞鐵枝狂毆，事主寡不敵眾，頭部和手及嚴重受傷，大量出血。兇徒得手後四散而逃，途人見狀報警。救護員將傷者送院急救，情況危殆，警方列作襲擊案。 <br />\n<br />\n至昨午5時46分，傷者傷重不治，交由西九龍總區反黑組調查。調查顯示，案件涉及大角咀聚居的巴基斯坦聲請者生活圈，死者生前與一名同樣持「行街紙」巴漢結仇，兩人原本是一起逃離家鄉來港「搵食」的朋友，卻因利益紛爭反目成仇，有人糾黨尋仇，令事主死於同鄉刀下。反黑組探員於昨晚7時許，掩至大角咀拘捕一名巴籍聲請漢，並於另一地點再拘一名涉嫌南亞漢。"},{"pid":"82ec23239c83ee327d5e9b4159e4bed23249a28e","tid":177702,"uid":72321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:52:01.000Z","msg":"一次過冇21件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04db4d85eab84788f7cf7b521a005c398dc2ea57","tid":177702,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:52:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da86212fa98d21ed2900200ff061d9c5d7aaf950","tid":177702,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:53:15.000Z","msg":"可唔可以遺返佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係到搞完事仲要養埋佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19a6c31178f4cfd7dbb9651936ff45e00ab237b6","tid":177702,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:53:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同鄉好波"},{"pid":"0d2a1969bead9efc99624a472c2f39570f22cc30","tid":177702,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:56:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"882267bbe5ee919a9c2c666b580b949a55921b9e","tid":177702,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:58:48.000Z","msg":"蝻亞 加一分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"030062c6410c0215a7530619c06917d888b9b204","tid":177702,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:02:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b0dd6cccb99afb2af6d5faedfd35116e7653be8","tid":177702,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:06:08.000Z","msg":"AZIZ 點讀 ???<br />\n<br />\nBTW, 巴基斯坦佬好鐘意溝賓賓, 話好好砌"},{"pid":"b19cfe63b36c4ac5d98b73a544dacdfbc0349e13","tid":177702,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:17:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c766a70efa7a6cf0ff2727fc1416ad73bbf9a5","tid":177702,"uid":2445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:19:08.000Z","msg":"葉問都要收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f06a4144f65b05a1fa9d4e181dfc616d8a68e9e","tid":177702,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T07:49:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7863c3062de070a98bf53e5f36819a90517ccd7","tid":177702,"uid":51796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T07:56:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/d5uqzbto\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fd5uqzbto&h=22cc39ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b594a6fe47f8b7aad74f474